name: TINGUS
description: TINGUS is a Solana-based art project that has recently made the leap into the Web3 space by transitioning into a coin. As the first step in this new venture, TINGUS plans to launch a 5,000-piece NFT collection, offering investors the chance to join the community as official holders. The project is entirely centered around MasterTingus, an artist who consistently creates and releases new TINGUS-themed artwork daily.
